{"tid":1447682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「荃灣人注意」荃灣西綠色小巴87k極深藍","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:46.000Z","uid":140710,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"89b91c19bafd62594d87b9bb76ea959b758626c1","tid":1447682,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"我只係一個小小嘅香港市民，小小嘅荃灣人。<br />\n發夢開始至今，我出嘅力唔算多，好少發聲，<br />\n但我一直默默支持。<br />\n<br />\n今日啱啱11點幾放工係西鐵站搭87k翻屋企，本來係好平常嘅事，<br />\n但我因爲見到呢件事，真係頂唔撚緊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母你憑咩話人係暴動！<br />\n當自己法官呀？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsX7s2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsX7s2C.jpg&h=16175ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eryeSum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeryeSum.png&h=c16c1be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲打，有咩方法可以狙擊呢條小巴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷搭有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係嬲撚到痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：第一次開po，1999請輕屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再利：仲有影低車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇左87k，仲有好撚多車可以翻屋企。<br />\n冇左香港，就冇得再翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09aa1030a8db38a20ab0bd1f5242110a0a8f4091","tid":1447682,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求下各位手足一齊諗辦法"},{"pid":"972996651f0253cda08fc71d846e10f38ea37e6d","tid":1447682,"uid":199816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"集體PM民陣發起大遊行<br />\n<br />\n和理非大遊行<br />\n<br />\n(幫下手散出去👆🏿)"},{"pid":"0e2b761fee4387c60ab1a3ebc8cb1c445c8ccc82","tid":1447682,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"睇完今日黑警啲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解仲會怪手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有冇良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad63ffb17a57baa622db147ce4de401e6d3c95ee","tid":1447682,"uid":16702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"有人俾人打呀"},{"pid":"5dbb8e0029f2732f9441ce07e19f9f43b5db1a63","tid":1447682,"uid":250951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n各位荃灣人小心唔好搭"},{"pid":"a0362f1aac96d258f2f0fe778471a69bdde38441","tid":1447682,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad63ffb17a57baa622db147ce4de401e6d3c95ee","tid":1447682,"uid":16702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"有人俾人打呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"有呀 咪係我地啲兄弟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667ba2d645ed9dba9bff26eae3a26b70857c79e2","tid":1447682,"uid":98773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯<br />\n係警察暴動"},{"pid":"5df9809b925a693be97bbd2fea9079976eb6bc76","tid":1447682,"uid":140710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dbb